1
00:00:53,854 --> 00:00:57,425
Project Loki starts with Lorelei
Rios transferring to Pampanga,

2
00:00:57,425 --> 00:01:01,061
where she meets the cold
and eccentric Loki Mendez,

3
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:03,597
who also happens to be her roommate.

4
00:01:03,597 --> 00:01:06,434
She later joins the QED Club,

5
00:01:06,434 --> 00:01:09,870
and the two eventually
become a crime-solving duo.

6
00:01:09,870 --> 00:01:15,009
Later in the story, Jamie Santiago
and Alistair Ravena join them,

7
00:01:15,009 --> 00:01:20,347
and together they hunt the elusive
mastermind known only as “M.”

8
00:01:20,347 --> 00:01:22,349
When I was writing Project Loki,

9
00:01:22,349 --> 00:01:27,254
I was heavily inspired by Sherlock
Holmes and Detective Conan.

10
00:01:27,254 --> 00:01:35,029
These two works inspired me
to write detective stories

11
00:01:35,029 --> 00:01:38,666
and come up with cases that
the characters would solve.

12
00:01:38,666 --> 00:01:43,671
One of my dreams as a writer is
to see my story adapted for the screen,

13
00:01:43,671 --> 00:01:45,539
whether as a series or a movie.

14
00:01:45,539 --> 00:01:53,380
I’m also happy that
VivaOne became our partner

15
00:01:53,380 --> 00:01:58,152
because they show great respect,
not just for me as a writer

16
00:01:58,152 --> 00:02:00,020
but also for the source material.

17
00:03:20,371 --> 00:03:23,543
It feels very overwhelming.

18
00:03:23,837 --> 00:03:28,508
Until now, I’m still surprised that
I got the role in Project Loki.

19
00:03:28,522 --> 00:03:30,276
But I’m very happy, very blessed,

20
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:34,228
and very determined to
give justice to the role of Loki.

21
00:03:34,228 --> 00:03:37,017
I’m very excited to show it to everyone.

22
00:03:37,041 --> 00:03:39,419
I know this role is challenging.

23
00:03:40,313 --> 00:03:41,554
The character is very different,

24
00:03:41,578 --> 00:03:45,125
and the genre is different from
the usual series people watch.

25
00:03:45,149 --> 00:03:46,707
It’s very interesting,

26
00:03:46,707 --> 00:03:50,940
and I’m really looking forward to
learning a lot from the director,

27
00:03:50,964 --> 00:03:57,337
my co-actors, and the producers—
everyone involved in Project Loki.

28
00:03:57,361 --> 00:04:04,911
Loki plays a big role, and despite
being mysterious, nonchalant and cold,

29
00:04:04,935 --> 00:04:09,382
he still brings purpose
to everything he does,

30
00:04:09,406 --> 00:04:17,490
with his investigations and
cases together with co-actors

31
00:04:22,811 --> 00:04:27,968
Of course, I feel extremely honored
to be able to take on this role.

32
00:04:28,697 --> 00:04:33,053
I consider really a big
responsibility for me because

33
00:04:33,054 --> 00:04:35,776
as an original Wattpad fan myself,

34
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:40,395
I know how much this means to readers.

35
00:04:40,395 --> 00:04:45,567
I’m really excited to bring her character
to life in the best way that I can.

36
00:04:45,567 --> 00:04:49,371
Like I said earlier,
I’m really, really excited.

37
00:04:49,371 --> 00:04:52,908
From the moment the project
was pitched to me,

38
00:04:52,908 --> 00:04:58,031
my excitement immediately peaked.

39
00:04:58,055 --> 00:05:00,282
I immediately read the book,

40
00:05:00,282 --> 00:05:07,789
and one thing I’m most excited about
is staying faithful to the series.

41
00:05:07,789 --> 00:05:11,011
and really do what I can do.

42
00:05:11,035 --> 00:05:13,993
You know, bring or give glory, justice,

43
00:05:14,017 --> 00:05:18,266
in terms of fleshing out her character

44
00:05:18,266 --> 00:05:20,468
in having people to get to know her more.

45
00:05:20,468 --> 00:05:25,859
It’s exciting for me, especially now that
I’m also a fan of Project Loki.

46
00:05:25,883 --> 00:05:28,362
After reading the book,

47
00:05:28,386 --> 00:05:32,399
I truly understood why
readers love this series so much.

48
00:05:32,423 --> 00:05:39,354
It’s really different from
any project I’ve ever done.

49
00:05:39,354 --> 00:05:46,761
It’s a great challenge as an actress
and pushes me outside my comfort zone.

50
00:05:46,761 --> 00:05:51,600
Things I never thought I could actually do.

51
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:55,870
Things I never imagined I’d be
able to pull off, especially here.

52
00:05:55,870 --> 00:06:05,180
It’s really cool that we’re exploring
different genres here in the Philippines.

53
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:08,350
It’s really exciting.

54
00:06:08,350 --> 00:06:14,908
I already know this will be one of
my favorite projects I’ll ever work on.

55
00:06:19,862 --> 00:06:24,233
They asked me if I was
interested in Project Loki

56
00:06:24,233 --> 00:06:30,072
I looked up Project Loki online
when I was asked about it.

57
00:06:30,072 --> 00:06:33,175
And I’m happy if I can be
completely honest,

58
00:06:33,175 --> 00:06:37,146
I liked that it wasn’t a
typical love-team story.

59
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:40,633
It was more mysterious.

60
00:06:42,165 --> 00:06:44,768
It was an edge to the show.

61
00:06:45,391 --> 00:06:51,431
I’m really happy they thought of
casting me in this Project Loki.

62
00:06:51,431 --> 00:06:54,434
When I read the book,

63
00:06:54,434 --> 00:06:58,404
I noticed that my character
is the oldest among the cast

64
00:06:58,404 --> 00:07:02,208
I play the older brother to
Dylan Menor in the story.

65
00:07:02,208 --> 00:07:04,777
So when I found out I was the brother,

66
00:07:04,777 --> 00:07:09,182
I noticed during the shoot that
I was a bit older than the others.

67
00:07:09,182 --> 00:07:11,718
Not that I really thought of it that way,

68
00:07:11,718 --> 00:07:14,921
but since it was a new cast,

69
00:07:14,921 --> 00:07:18,414
I guess I was just used
to doing university series.

70
00:07:18,438 --> 00:07:22,342
They’re my friends,
I’m already comfortable.

71
00:07:22,366 --> 00:07:24,944
And now it’s a new whole cast,

72
00:07:24,968 --> 00:07:30,970
and I felt that I was the one who
is extracted in University Series,

73
00:07:30,994 --> 00:07:33,730
and put here in Project Loki.

74
00:07:33,754 --> 00:07:37,657
So of course, I was still adjusting
to being around new people.

75
00:07:38,844 --> 00:07:45,350
I’m still careful around them, which
fits the “distant older brother” vibe.

76
00:07:50,355 --> 00:07:52,090
Of course, I was super excited.

77
00:07:52,090 --> 00:07:55,694
Another character, another project,
another blessing.

78
00:07:56,041 --> 00:08:03,048
I’m grateful because I never expected
to be accepted here, as Jamie

79
00:08:03,048 --> 00:08:07,986
I prepared mentally, physically,
and emotionally for the role.

80
00:08:07,986 --> 00:08:13,705
I also study Jamie’s mannerisms,
her character description.

81
00:08:13,729 --> 00:08:14,861
I read it, I repeat it.

82
00:08:14,885 --> 00:08:18,765
I do research because I want
to understand her personality.

83
00:08:24,398 --> 00:08:28,241
I’m super happy, and at the same time,
I can’t believe it.

84
00:08:29,604 --> 00:08:33,141
At first, I didn’t really
read Project Loki,

85
00:08:33,141 --> 00:08:36,978
but I heard from my friends
that the story is really good.

86
00:08:37,745 --> 00:08:40,086
While I was auditioning, I thought,

87
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:43,790
“What if I get into this series?
My friends would be so happy.”

88
00:08:44,185 --> 00:08:50,358
It’s also a blessing for me because
Project Loki is well-known.

89
00:08:51,259 --> 00:08:54,595
Super blessed and excited for this role.

90
00:08:54,595 --> 00:08:59,233
Well, this is where my range
as an actor will really be tested.

91
00:08:59,233 --> 00:09:02,270
Pretty exciting,
but at the same time nervous.

92
00:09:16,717 --> 00:09:23,057
First of all, I want to greet
all the Project Loki fans.

93
00:09:23,057 --> 00:09:26,928
because I know they’ve
been expecting this and,

94
00:09:26,928 --> 00:09:30,179
they’re looking forward to this project.

95
00:09:30,203 --> 00:09:32,572
So the expectation that I have is,

96
00:09:32,572 --> 00:09:34,507
for the actors to do their homework,

97
00:09:34,531 --> 00:09:39,512
because AkoSiIbarra did the four chapters,

98
00:09:39,536 --> 00:09:43,083
like I really, really expect them to

99
00:09:43,084 --> 00:09:45,987
really know the character inside and out.

100
00:09:45,987 --> 00:09:50,590
and how they’re gonna
make it into a real person.

101
00:09:50,596 --> 00:09:52,826
Because imagination is one thing,

102
00:09:52,850 --> 00:09:59,476
reading it is another, and portraying it
on screen is completely different.

103
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:02,870
Well, Director Xian is an actor,

104
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:07,483
so I expect to learn more
about acting in general.

105
00:10:07,507 --> 00:10:11,077
To him because he is a veteran,
seasoned actor.

106
00:10:11,101 --> 00:10:12,970
and with him being the director,

107
00:10:12,977 --> 00:10:15,703
for sure he will give me some tips,

108
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:18,918
some advices on how
I would portray Loki.

109
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:22,246
For sure gesture and nuances,

110
00:10:22,819 --> 00:10:26,435
how will I deliver lines or expressions,

111
00:10:26,459 --> 00:10:29,284
for sure, he will guide me.

112
00:10:29,308 --> 00:10:32,813
with the help also of
my co-stars/co-actors.

113
00:10:32,837 --> 00:10:35,070
I’m expecting a lot to him.

114
00:10:35,094 --> 00:10:39,533
I’m really, really excited
to learn from him,

115
00:10:39,557 --> 00:10:42,409
well someone who dwells in directing,

116
00:10:42,433 --> 00:10:43,777
as well in music videos.

117
00:10:43,801 --> 00:10:46,747
But for one day,
I would love to become a director

118
00:10:46,771 --> 00:10:49,282
in the field of film and TV.

119
00:10:49,858 --> 00:10:52,152
I’m excited to learn from his vision.

120
00:10:52,176 --> 00:10:56,323
Also, I consider that
we are blessed as a cast

121
00:10:56,328 --> 00:10:59,969
to have not only a director like him,

122
00:10:59,993 --> 00:11:03,156
but also an actor for the director.

123
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:07,834
He is such a brilliant actor
in his own rights.

124
00:11:07,858 --> 00:11:14,196
So, I’m very excited
to learn his techniques,

125
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:17,677
and tricks that he learned along
the way throughout his career.

126
00:11:17,701 --> 00:11:22,892
Also, I’m excited besides his wisdom,

127
00:11:22,916 --> 00:11:26,699
to be able to bond with him
through our shared experience,

128
00:11:26,723 --> 00:11:28,188
being in this craft,

129
00:11:28,212 --> 00:11:31,925
I really do believe that this
give us a huge advantage.

130
00:11:31,949 --> 00:11:34,861
Our director knows exactly
what we’re going through,

131
00:11:34,885 --> 00:11:37,497
and what it’s like to be in our shoes.

132
00:11:37,521 --> 00:11:39,499
We’re all working close together.

133
00:11:39,523 --> 00:11:42,602
We’re playing around different emotions.

134
00:11:42,626 --> 00:11:46,140
We’re playing around a different
character background.

135
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:51,344
So, it’s real something
to look forward to,

136
00:11:51,368 --> 00:11:58,018
to all the Project Loki fans
because of characters’ richness.

137
00:11:58,042 --> 00:11:59,686
so expect the best

138
00:11:59,710 --> 00:12:01,288
from the actors

139
00:12:01,298 --> 00:12:02,733
who will be portraying

140
00:12:02,733 --> 00:12:04,125
the QED 4

141
00:12:04,149 --> 00:12:05,178
even

142
00:12:05,202 --> 00:12:06,359
even all the

143
00:12:07,192 --> 00:12:09,361
all the special characters involved.

144
00:12:09,361 --> 00:12:10,629
I don't want to say too much,

145
00:12:10,629 --> 00:12:11,629
but yeah,

146
00:12:11,654 --> 00:12:12,731
expect

147
00:12:12,731 --> 00:12:14,500
their 100%

148
00:12:17,069 --> 00:12:19,671
And Dylan is our Loki.

149
00:12:19,671 --> 00:12:20,706
Everybody!

150
00:12:22,208 --> 00:12:23,208
Jayda!

151
00:12:26,467 --> 00:12:29,015
Room or apartment 302.

152
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,961
Our apartment.

153
00:12:36,025 --> 00:12:38,627
That’s when he says… [inaudible]

154
00:12:48,673 --> 00:12:52,448
Hello… a little bit of
presence of mind, right?

155
00:12:52,448 --> 00:12:53,482
Extend your patience.

156
00:12:55,704 --> 00:12:56,704
Was it better?

157
00:13:00,556 --> 00:13:01,690
1, 2, 3…

158
00:13:02,982 --> 00:13:06,419
Yeah! Thank you guys!

159
00:13:15,874 --> 00:13:18,849
Guys, this is Jayda. She sang “Babala.”

160
00:13:19,098 --> 00:13:20,333
Please stream “Babala.”

161
00:13:20,357 --> 00:13:22,244
Right! That’s right!

162
00:13:22,268 --> 00:13:23,803
That’s my soundtrip.

163
00:13:23,828 --> 00:13:24,828
Nice!

164
00:13:32,507 --> 00:13:34,509
And this, we’ll only do it…

165
00:13:44,775 --> 00:13:46,392
Alright!

166
00:13:50,147 --> 00:13:51,449
Okay, let’s smile.

167
00:13:54,986 --> 00:13:55,986
Go over there!

168
00:13:57,455 --> 00:13:58,805
Just act if you want!

169
00:13:59,210 --> 00:14:03,676
Act if you want or mouth the lyrics
if that’s your thing. Up to you.

170
00:14:05,029 --> 00:14:06,029
He was surprised!

171
00:14:06,263 --> 00:14:07,398
He was surprised,
you suddenly started singing.

172
00:14:10,948 --> 00:14:12,470
Pack up!

173
00:14:17,659 --> 00:14:18,827
Next one! Next one!

174
00:14:24,139 --> 00:14:25,674
I was extremely happy

175
00:14:25,674 --> 00:14:27,500
and the first thing I
did was thank the Lord

176
00:14:27,524 --> 00:14:30,569
because this is a new role for me

177
00:14:30,593 --> 00:14:32,304
I like challenging roles.

178
00:14:32,328 --> 00:14:36,103
I'm happy and blessed that
the Lord has granted me

179
00:14:36,127 --> 00:14:38,444
the opportunity to
have a role like this

180
00:14:38,468 --> 00:14:43,360
It’s an honor to be part of
the adaptation of Project Loki

181
00:14:43,384 --> 00:14:45,551
And this story is really beautiful

182
00:14:45,575 --> 00:14:48,287
I’m nervous but also excited

183
00:14:48,311 --> 00:14:49,765
because many people support

184
00:14:49,765 --> 00:14:52,001
and read Project Loki.

185
00:14:52,001 --> 00:14:55,771
I’m very excited to bring the
character of Stein Alberts to life

186
00:14:55,771 --> 00:14:57,029
Hi, everyone!

187
00:14:57,830 --> 00:14:59,398
I'm really, really excited

188
00:14:59,422 --> 00:15:00,709
to play Rosetta…

189
00:15:00,709 --> 00:15:08,217
and I hope my performance
gives justice to the character.

190
00:15:08,217 --> 00:15:11,253
When we posted during the go-see,

191
00:15:11,253 --> 00:15:14,456
I had a photo holding Rosetta’s script.

192
00:15:14,810 --> 00:15:17,413
Someone messaged me

193
00:15:17,413 --> 00:15:19,869
saying I really looked
like Rosetta,

194
00:15:19,893 --> 00:15:25,187
and that’s when I realized
how big this project is.

195
00:15:25,187 --> 00:15:28,624
It’s a mix of pressure and excitement.

196
00:15:28,624 --> 00:15:33,529
I usually play demure role

197
00:15:33,529 --> 00:15:37,333
but this time the character is
a bit playful, which excites me.

198
00:15:37,333 --> 00:15:39,019
I'm really excited to do this

199
00:15:39,043 --> 00:15:44,177
Until now, I still can’t believe
I got the role of Rhea.

200
00:15:44,190 --> 00:15:46,835
Everything still feels surreal

201
00:15:46,859 --> 00:15:49,598
This is only my second acting project

202
00:15:49,622 --> 00:15:52,886
I’m used to performing—dancing and singing.

203
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:56,856
I’m a former girl group member,
so this is very new to me.

204
00:15:56,880 --> 00:16:01,027
It’s exciting and nerve-wracking
at the same time.

205
00:16:01,028 --> 00:16:09,708
I was nervous because Margarette
is a major character.

206
00:16:10,705 --> 00:16:14,249
I got nervous and felt a bit pressured.

207
00:16:14,273 --> 00:16:19,712
I started reading the book
to fully understand the story.

208
00:16:19,712 --> 00:16:23,549
while I was reading,
I genuinely enjoyed reading it.

209
00:16:23,573 --> 00:16:29,555
For the project Loki readers,
I am just excited as you guys are

210
00:16:29,555 --> 00:16:34,594
We promise to give justice to
the characters you imagined.

211
00:16:34,594 --> 00:16:37,897
Of course, I’m happy to
be part of a new project,

212
00:16:37,921 --> 00:16:40,133
but I’m also nervous because

213
00:16:40,157 --> 00:16:46,138
I know the Wattpad readers are super,
super invested in the characters.

214
00:16:46,145 --> 00:16:47,145
All I'm hoping is that

215
00:16:47,170 --> 00:16:48,348
we can all give a Justice

216
00:16:48,348 --> 00:16:49,782
I can give a justice

217
00:16:49,782 --> 00:16:53,879
I hope they’ll like what
we’ll do in the show.

218
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,922
I’m really excited

219
00:16:55,922 --> 00:16:59,225
knowing that Project Loki
has such a huge fanbase,

220
00:16:59,225 --> 00:17:01,861
and even more excited to be part of it!

221
00:17:01,861 --> 00:17:04,898
I’ve read the book as well,

222
00:17:04,898 --> 00:17:09,002
and honestly, it feels more like a
detective thriller than a love story.

223
00:17:09,002 --> 00:17:14,233
And it feels really nice to
step out of the love team.

224
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:18,647
I'm really excited for this role.

225
00:17:18,671 --> 00:17:21,297
This is going to be
my big break, somehow.

226
00:17:21,321 --> 00:17:28,448
Because I'm going to meet a lot of people
and learn a lot of things from this role.

227
00:17:28,799 --> 00:17:31,268
At first, I was really excited.

228
00:17:31,268 --> 00:17:34,171
But right now it's finally syncing in.

229
00:17:34,171 --> 00:17:35,640
I'm still nervous.

230
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:39,469
But I'm more excited.

231
00:17:39,493 --> 00:17:44,139
I’m really excited to portray Bastien.

232
00:17:44,163 --> 00:17:46,899
My character here is very interesting

233
00:17:46,923 --> 00:17:49,235
and I can't wait to show it to you guys.

234
00:17:50,269 --> 00:17:57,009
Actually I feel overwhelmed and nervous
because I read the book...

235
00:17:57,033 --> 00:18:00,407
like a year ago or two years ago,
and I know how popular it is.

236
00:18:00,431 --> 00:18:06,952
It’s the most popular mystery story
on Wattpad in the Philippines.

237
00:18:08,487 --> 00:18:11,934
I want to give justice to the character

238
00:18:11,958 --> 00:18:15,622
because if you don't,

239
00:18:15,646 --> 00:18:22,030
it might give a bad impression
to the story and production.

240
00:18:22,054 --> 00:18:24,503
It's overwhelming,
but at the same time exciting.

241
00:18:24,527 --> 00:18:26,805
The character I'm playing,
Hershel Aguirre...

242
00:18:26,829 --> 00:18:30,896
he is not like the front runner
who is solving the mystery.

243
00:18:30,896 --> 00:18:38,103
He is more of the science guy
or the guy behind the QED 4 team.

244
00:18:38,409 --> 00:18:44,032
He is actually plays a pivotal
and important role.

245
00:18:44,056 --> 00:18:46,292
He is not recurring

246
00:18:46,316 --> 00:18:48,227
but he is a fan favorite,

247
00:18:48,251 --> 00:18:52,831
based on comments on Wattpad
as I've read the story.

248
00:18:52,855 --> 00:18:56,135
And I think the Hershel
character is important

249
00:18:56,159 --> 00:18:58,504
and pivotal for the timeline.

250
00:19:00,219 --> 00:19:01,219
Hi!

251
00:19:02,755 --> 00:19:03,755
Hi!

252
00:19:04,023 --> 00:19:05,023
Hello!

253
00:19:26,278 --> 00:19:27,366
So there… left, left…

254
00:19:27,391 --> 00:19:28,422
Yes, here.

255
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:29,430
Okay, so here.

256
00:19:30,293 --> 00:19:31,293
Okay.

257
00:19:42,772 --> 00:19:43,772
Behind the scenes.

258
00:19:46,909 --> 00:19:48,077
She doesn’t know you, dude!

259
00:19:57,974 --> 00:19:59,781
Just fix your hair.

260
00:20:01,057 --> 00:20:03,603
You might have been sweaty
at that time, so you did this…

261
00:20:05,461 --> 00:20:07,240
You’re that unbothered, I guess.

262
00:20:20,343 --> 00:20:22,845
You have something to do
to him that disables him.

263
00:20:31,987 --> 00:20:32,987
He’s like...

264
00:20:33,489 --> 00:20:35,325
What am I gonna do? I can’t..

265
00:20:35,743 --> 00:20:37,127
It’s not possible.

266
00:20:44,376 --> 00:20:46,945
I don't want to pre-empt the scene,

267
00:20:46,969 --> 00:20:49,050
but there's one thing that
I'm looking forward to is...

268
00:20:49,074 --> 00:20:50,249
I'll just describe it.

269
00:20:52,003 --> 00:20:53,070
To avoid spoiling the scene.

270
00:20:53,094 --> 00:20:55,706
It would be the chair scene.

271
00:20:59,225 --> 00:21:02,161
I’m really looking forward
to the chair scene,

272
00:21:02,161 --> 00:21:06,733
as well as there's a scene involving Lori

273
00:21:07,007 --> 00:21:08,375
and they drum.

274
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:11,378
And one more.

275
00:21:11,378 --> 00:21:14,206
One last is the drinking tea.

276
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:18,351
So those are key moments that I think...

277
00:21:19,152 --> 00:21:20,387
will be...

278
00:21:20,987 --> 00:21:22,989
I'm really excited to shoot.

279
00:21:22,989 --> 00:21:28,528
If there’s one thing I can promise,
especially when it comes to the actors…

280
00:21:28,528 --> 00:21:38,831
Each director has their own sensibilities,
and some approach things differently.

281
00:21:38,855 --> 00:21:40,666
The promise I make to my actors is this

282
00:21:40,690 --> 00:21:48,279
I’ve gone through the grind,
and I’m still going through it on

283
00:21:48,303 --> 00:21:52,586
this journey of becoming
and growing as an actor.

284
00:21:52,586 --> 00:21:56,158
I promised the actors
we’ll figure this out together.

285
00:21:56,182 --> 00:21:57,717
They don’t have to be scared

286
00:21:57,741 --> 00:22:01,457
I know what it feels like to be on set.

287
00:22:01,481 --> 00:22:05,524
Day 1, I already felt the pressure

288
00:22:05,548 --> 00:22:10,096
of having to play the
character given to you

289
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:12,552
You have the fans’ expectations,

290
00:22:12,576 --> 00:22:14,533
the producers’ expectations,

291
00:22:14,557 --> 00:22:18,291
and of course,
your own expectations for yourself.

292
00:22:18,316 --> 00:22:22,141
It’s just a challenge,
and I want them to embrace it.

293
00:22:22,157 --> 00:22:23,952
That’s what I promise them

294
00:22:23,976 --> 00:22:26,883
that we’re all holding hands
together in this project.

295
00:22:26,907 --> 00:22:28,047
And we’re going to work

296
00:22:28,071 --> 00:22:30,149
our way into making this

297
00:22:30,173 --> 00:22:38,113
the best version it can be,
to really give it justice.

298
00:22:38,126 --> 00:22:43,064
so as far as my journey as a director

299
00:22:43,064 --> 00:22:51,405
It’s going to be a challenge to translate
the book into this adaptation.

300
00:22:53,174 --> 00:22:56,611
I want the fans to feel at ease.

301
00:22:56,611 --> 00:23:00,912
And I want them to know our promise

302
00:23:00,936 --> 00:23:03,782
that we’re here to do our best

303
00:23:03,807 --> 00:23:12,058
and deliver the best
version of Project Loki.

304
00:24:02,975 --> 00:24:05,978
We can assure you that
it will remain faithful

305
00:24:05,978 --> 00:24:08,047
to the structure of the source material.

306
00:24:08,071 --> 00:24:11,205
So you don’t have to
worry about it deviating

307
00:24:11,229 --> 00:24:13,453
from what you already know and love.

308
00:24:13,477 --> 00:24:17,657
So rest assured—the story you loved

309
00:24:17,681 --> 00:24:19,926
is the same story you will be watching.

310
00:24:20,319 --> 00:24:22,292
For me, we just want to
give justice to the story

311
00:24:22,322 --> 00:24:25,531
and stay true to
the source material.

312
00:24:25,765 --> 00:24:30,336
We didn’t just take Project Loki
and change the story.

313
00:24:30,360 --> 00:24:35,140
We will do our best to execute it
as closely as possible.

314
00:24:35,164 --> 00:24:38,544
You will see your favorite characters
brought to life, in the flesh.

315
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:43,907
I thought I couldn’t be more excited
for this project than I already was.

316
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:47,119
But somehow, I became even more
motivated to do this project.

317
00:24:47,143 --> 00:24:50,923
We truly feel your love and support.

318
00:24:50,947 --> 00:24:52,525
So thank you so, so much.

319
00:24:52,549 --> 00:24:55,661
We just want to give you a good show,
and I’m really excited.

320
00:24:55,685 --> 00:24:58,219
I’m excited and nervous
at the same time,

321
00:24:58,243 --> 00:25:00,742
and of course, happy to
be part of Project Loki.

322
00:25:00,766 --> 00:25:03,335
I’m excited for you to
see Project Loki soon.

323
00:25:03,335 --> 00:25:07,005
I hope you enjoy and appreciate
the scenes we worked on.

324
00:25:07,005 --> 00:25:10,576
It’s a new genre—something to
look forward to, and very interesting.

325
00:25:10,576 --> 00:25:14,279
It was the first time we had a meeting
like this after a press conference.

326
00:25:14,313 --> 00:25:18,050
Where we actually got
to sit down with the writer.

327
00:25:18,150 --> 00:25:20,919
And we were able to ask
all the questions we had.

328
00:25:21,119 --> 00:25:24,071
It helped clear all our
doubts about the character.

329
00:25:24,095 --> 00:25:27,893
I hope we do it well—it’s exciting.

330
00:25:27,917 --> 00:25:30,329
Before we went out, I was already nervous.

331
00:25:30,353 --> 00:25:32,364
I was extremely nervous,
I don’t know why.

332
00:25:32,364 --> 00:25:38,604
But I’m happy because the
people welcomed us warmly.

333
00:25:39,661 --> 00:25:41,896
Guys, please watch out
for me as Jamie Santiago.

334
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:44,076
I’ll give my best—
she’s a very complex character.

335
00:25:44,101 --> 00:25:45,267
This is my first time
doing something like this.

336
00:25:45,267 --> 00:25:48,904
I’m very grateful and
excited to start taping.

337
00:25:49,571 --> 00:25:54,863
I’m very excited to work with Jada,
Marco, Dylan, and the rest of the cast.

338
00:25:54,887 --> 00:25:55,988
Grateful and blessed.

339
00:25:56,012 --> 00:26:00,559
To all Wattpad readers,
I won’t be fake with you.

340
00:26:00,583 --> 00:26:02,561
I hope you give me a chance.

341
00:26:02,585 --> 00:26:06,261
I know that at first, with
Calix,

342
00:26:06,285 --> 00:26:10,903
some of you had doubts about
whether I could pull it off well.

343
00:26:10,903 --> 00:26:12,638
I gave my all.

344
00:26:12,638 --> 00:26:16,375
I hope this time in my new
project called, Project Loki.

345
00:26:17,511 --> 00:26:20,748
It’s a new project that came in to my life.

346
00:26:20,748 --> 00:26:26,587
I know this might be a very big,
important book for you guys.

347
00:26:28,322 --> 00:26:30,257
I promise that I will give my best.

348
00:26:31,392 --> 00:26:34,528
With the help of Viva,
with the help of Director Xian,

349
00:26:34,962 --> 00:26:36,030
We’ll give it our all,

350
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:39,800
and we hope we can capture Luthor’s flair.

351
00:26:39,800 --> 00:26:41,068
Hi readers.

352
00:26:41,919 --> 00:26:44,153
I just want to tell you that

353
00:26:44,177 --> 00:26:49,407
I’ll do my absolute best to
do justice for Jaimie Santiago.

354
00:26:50,042 --> 00:26:52,711
I hope you’ll watch out for me as Jaimie.

355
00:26:52,735 --> 00:26:55,282
I won’t let you down.

356
00:26:55,282 --> 00:26:58,986
To all the readers of Project Loki,

357
00:26:58,986 --> 00:27:02,322
I hope you’ll support us.

358
00:27:03,424 --> 00:27:07,027
It will be a great, great series.

359
00:27:07,027 --> 00:27:08,929
Stay tuned for us!

360
00:27:08,929 --> 00:27:13,867
To all the Wattpad fans,
expect that we are going to do our best.

361
00:27:14,835 --> 00:27:16,970
To the best of our ability,

362
00:27:16,970 --> 00:27:18,839
All of that has already been taken care of.

363
00:27:19,373 --> 00:27:25,012
So we will do whatever it takes to give
justice to all the characters you loved.

364
00:27:25,546 --> 00:27:30,384
For all the scenes that really tugged
at your emotions,

365
00:27:30,951 --> 00:27:32,486
That’s our promise.

366
00:27:32,486 --> 00:27:34,888
We will give you a good one.

367
00:27:34,888 --> 00:27:37,024
We promise to give you a good one.

368
00:27:37,024 --> 00:27:39,660
I just want to thank to
all the Wattpad readers,

369
00:27:39,660 --> 00:27:41,195
and to the fans of Project Loki,

370
00:27:41,195 --> 00:27:44,070
for the warm reception
of the announcement

371
00:27:44,094 --> 00:27:47,944
that there will be an
adaptation of my story.

372
00:27:47,968 --> 00:27:49,348
To all the old time readers,

373
00:27:49,372 --> 00:27:54,641
rest assured that what you have read
is what you will see on screen.

374
00:27:54,641 --> 00:27:57,511
It will be faithful to the source material.

375
00:27:57,511 --> 00:28:01,248
And for the new viewers or audience,

376
00:28:01,248 --> 00:28:05,452
This is a nice change
for your watching habits.

377
00:28:07,054 --> 00:28:10,557
I hope you support and you
will like the genre of mystery

378
00:28:10,557 --> 00:28:14,394
because this genre is also very rich.

379
00:28:14,394 --> 00:28:19,066
To all the PLayers of Project Loki,

380
00:28:19,066 --> 00:28:23,504
I just want to say,
I hope we can make you proud

381
00:28:23,504 --> 00:28:27,674
that you will love this series
as much as we do, as much I do.

382
00:28:28,475 --> 00:28:35,482
Now I can already say that
this is something to look out for.

383
00:28:35,862 --> 00:28:39,087
At the end of the day we just
want to give you a good show.

384
00:28:39,336 --> 00:28:44,199
To bring this beloved story by AkoSiIbarra
to life, in the best way we can.

385
00:28:44,224 --> 00:28:45,759
So I hope guys you enjoy this.

386
00:28:45,759 --> 00:28:49,163
For the Wattpad readers who
are supporting Project Loki,

387
00:28:49,163 --> 00:28:52,166
to all who read this book
and will start to read it,

388
00:28:53,867 --> 00:28:58,172
we’re excited to finally
release Project Loki.

389
00:28:58,172 --> 00:29:04,278
We promise to do our best, to give
our best to portray our characters,

390
00:29:04,278 --> 00:29:08,615
and to give more life in our characters.

391
00:29:09,309 --> 00:29:10,692
We hope that you enjoy.

392
00:29:10,729 --> 00:29:16,831
We hope that you appreciate the art
we are doing for Project Loki.

393
00:29:17,925 --> 00:29:23,130
We’ve been doing it together with lots
of great artist, director, and producers.

394
00:29:23,997 --> 00:29:26,900
I’m also looking forward so
I hope you are looking forward.
